metadata.name: Jungle Arena #1
metadata.description: The Jungle Arena NFT was a rare and unique digital collectible, depicting a small ring hidden in a clearing, surrounded by tall grasses and wildflowers. It was fought over by many and finally won by a skilled warrior named Kaia who outmaneuvered and defeated her opponents. As the last lines of the NFT's code were transferred to Kaia, the message popped up on her screen ! 'You are now the proud owner of the Jungle arena NFT, display it with pride and join us for more exciting battles...'
